		<documentation>OvrC Sync Agent
		
The agent is used to synchronize changes that have occurred in the C4 system to update the OvrC environment. The agent will be automatically installed will while bootstrapping the project in OvrC. If installed from Composer, the agent will not work. Currently, only RYFF projects are supported.</documentation>
